    "description": "This moves all the logic for setting matplotlib font properties in `PlotWindow` and `PhasePlot` into the `PlotContainer` base class.  Additionally, I've added the axes title text to the list of text objects we set the font properties for.\r\n\r\nLastly, I've fixed a bug in the `PhasePlot.set_title` function that made it so that it would only work properly when users specify fields via field tuples.\r\n\r\nHere's an example notebook made after applying this PR: http://nbviewer.ipython.org/gist/ngoldbaum/f83a3f24ad1ae31f1e20",
