            "content": {
                "raw": "Nice integration.  One quick related question (not holding up this PR): do people think we should have an `annotate_title()` for both `PlotWindow` and `PhasePlot` classes, instead of having similar functionality from two separate functions (i.e. `annotate_title()` and `set_title()`)?  Perhaps there is a good reason for this, but it seems like it would be better to replicate the same api for both classes.",
                "html": "<p>Nice integration.  One quick related question (not holding up this PR): do people think we should have an <code>annotate_title()</code> for both <code>PlotWindow</code> and <code>PhasePlot</code> classes, instead of having similar functionality from two separate functions (i.e. <code>annotate_title()</code> and <code>set_title()</code>)?  Perhaps there is a good reason for this, but it seems like it would be better to replicate the same api for both classes.</p>",
                "markup": "markdown"
            },
